{"data": [{"id": "4745673", "title": "First Solar Could Be Well Poised As A Future Leader In Renewable Energy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455762465/image_1455762465.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Abstract aerial/drone view over a field of solar panels at sunrise\" data-id=\"1455762465\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455762465/image_1455762465.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455762465/image_1455762465.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455762465/image_1455762465.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455762465/image_1455762465.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455762465/image_1455762465.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455762465/image_1455762465.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455762465/image_1455762465.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455762465/image_1455762465.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Justin Paget</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The renewable energy wave is in full swing, and despite an incoming Trump Presidency potentially pushing back to some degree on some elements of climate change policy, the sector looks to be one to watch for the coming decades. One of</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455762465/image_1455762465.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745673-first-solar-could-be-well-poised-as-a-future-leader-in-renewable-energy", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 23:25:22", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745670", "title": "Barrick Gold: Back On The Sale Rack (Rating Upgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1638258380/image_1638258380.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"native 1.05 gram gold nugget from Kenieba District, Mali, Africa\" data-id=\"1638258380\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1638258380/image_1638258380.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1638258380/image_1638258380.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1638258380/image_1638258380.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1638258380/image_1638258380.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1638258380/image_1638258380.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1638258380/image_1638258380.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1638258380/image_1638258380.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1638258380/image_1638258380.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Bjoern Wylezich</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><strong>All figures are in United States Dollars unless otherwise noted. G/T = grams per tonne (of gold or silver). GEOs = gold-equivalent ounces. SEOs = silver-equivalent ounces. AISC refers to all-in sustaining costs. LOMP = life of mine plan. TPD = tonnes per day.</strong></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1638258380/image_1638258380.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745670-barrick-gold-back-on-the-sale-rack-rating-upgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 23:09:31", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745664", "title": "S&P 500: Tensions Are High And Exits Are Crowded", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159126735/image_2159126735.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A double exposure image of skyscrapers with overlay of financial graphs, set against a blurred background, illustrating the concept of business growth\" data-id=\"2159126735\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159126735/image_2159126735.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159126735/image_2159126735.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159126735/image_2159126735.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159126735/image_2159126735.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159126735/image_2159126735.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159126735/image_2159126735.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159126735/image_2159126735.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159126735/image_2159126735.jpg?io=