ha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1179667626/image_1179667626.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1179667626/image_1179667626.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">courtneyk</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>People could be forgiven for thinking Yiren Digital Ltd (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/YRD\" title=\"Yiren Digital Ltd.\">YRD</a></span>) looks too good to be true. YRD is not only profitable and growing as a business, but it also looks cheap with the stock available at very low multiples. YRD, for</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1179667626/image_1179667626.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745669-yiren-digital-the-pros-outweigh-the-cons", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 22:55:04", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745666", "title": "The 2025 Outlook: A Bear Market And The S&P 500 At 4100", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1283384596/image_1283384596.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Bear Market\" data-id=\"1283384596\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"3964px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1283384596/image_1283384596.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1283384596/image_1283384596.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1283384596/image_1283384596.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1283384596/image_1283384596.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1283384596/image_1283384596.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1283384596/image_1283384596.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1283384596/image_1283384596.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1283384596/image_1283384596.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">DNY59</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>The Key Point</h2> <p>I expect a recessionary bear market in the S&amp;P 500 (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SPY\" title=\"SPDR\u00ae S&amp;P 500\u00ae ETF Trust\">SPY</a></span>) (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SP500\" class=\"ticker-link\">SP500</a>) in 2025, with a target level of 4100, which is around 30% below the current level.</p> <p>Here is the detailed analysis.</p> <h2>The consensus</h2>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1283384596/image_1283384596.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745666-the-2025-outlook-a-bear-market-and-the-s-and-p-500-at-4100", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 22:26:26", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745663", "title": "MicroStrategy And Its Bitcoin Business Deserve More Respect Than Many Are Giving It", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346043436/image_1346043436.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"5 floating Bitcoins\" data-id=\"1346043436\" data-type