"kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745661", "title": "No, Mr. Powell, A Recession Has Not Been Avoided", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1201610071/image_1201610071.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Planet Earth\" data-id=\"1201610071\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1201610071/image_1201610071.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1201610071/image_1201610071.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1201610071/image_1201610071.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1201610071/image_1201610071.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1201610071/image_1201610071.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1201610071/image_1201610071.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1201610071/image_1201610071.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1201610071/image_1201610071.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Daniel Grizelj</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Jerome Powell: \u201cI think it\u2019s pretty clear we\u2019ve avoided a recession\u201d</h2> <p>In response to a media member, who at Wednesday\u2019s post-FOMC press conference, asked Jerome Powell if he thinks we\u2019ve avoided the recession that everyone [read: the media and its obsession</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1201610071/image_1201610071.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745661-no-mr-powell-a-recession-has-not-been-avoided", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 22:10:09", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745658", "title": "Adobe: Our Top Idea For 2025 Now Trading At A 30% Discount To SaaS Peers", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1581810849/image_1581810849.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Adobe headquarters in San Jose, California, USA\" data-id=\"1581810849\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1581810849/image_1581810849.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1581810849/image_1581810849.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1581810849/image_1581810849.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1581810849/image_1581810849.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1581810849/image_1581810849.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1581810849/image_1581810849.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1581810849/image_1581810849.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1581810849/image_1581810849.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">JHVEPhoto</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Summary</h2> <p>We at Cash Flow Compounders look for high margin, low capital intensity businesses that are able to grow at above market rates. We especially like finding these when trading at sub-market multiples.</p> <p>Adobe fits the bill admirably today. While many</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1581810849/image_1581810849.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745658-adobe-top-idea-2025-now-trading-at-discount-to-saas-peers", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 22:05:24", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745655", "title": "The Real 'January Effect' And How To Play It", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161094997/image_2161094997.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Red mark on the calendar at January 2025\" data-id=\"2161094997\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1022px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161094997/image_2161094997.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161094997/image_2161094997.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161094997/image_2161094997.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161094997/image_2161094997.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161094997/image_2161094997.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161094997/image_2161094997.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161094997/image_2161094997.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161094997/image_2161094997.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">baona/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>As sure as you are reading this, the media will soon put out articles mentioning the well-known \u2018January Effect\u2019 \u2013 a calendar anomaly first presented in 1942 that supposedly bestows a positive performance edge to equities for the month</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161094997/image_2161094997.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745655-the-real-january-effect-and-how-to-play-it", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 21:54:40", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745653", "title": "Will Inflation Accelerate And Force The Fed To Hike Rates?", "description": "<p>\"Inflation is always and everywhere a monetary phenomenon.\u201d</p> <p>\u2014 Milton Friedman</p> <p>This famous quote from Nobel Prize-winning economist Milton Friedman means that only changes in the money supply drive inflation in the long run, while other factors might cause temporary price</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1609437977/image_1609437977.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745653-will-inflation-accelerate-and-force-the-fed-to-hike-rates", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 21:48:20", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}]}